post_text:
On Thursday, April 30th from 1-6 PM Seniors and/or their parents are invited to come to the High School and pick up a 2020 graduate yard sign, a senior gift from the parents, and a letter from Dr. Edwards with details on graduation.

Process:
Enter the parking lot through the North entrance and pull up to door #3 (Main entrance). A staff member will get your name and place the 3 items in the trunk of your car (pop your trunk or back lift gate when you pull up). Please do not get out of your vehicle.

Once you have received your items, please exit through the south exit.
